<font color="#FF0000">VISITING THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Sat Dec 27 22:56:15 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
<br>
Americans be proud of your wall! As an Australian Vietnam Veteran it brought tears to my eyes in 1994 when I was priviliged to walk back and forth for four days along the wall. I never knew an american killed personally but I still feel the sorrow.<br>
The wall reminds the world not just America of the great sacrifices made to enable the many countries of Asia to establish themselves.<br>
I am pround to have served and had your support.<br>
Len Hall<br>
Perth<br>
West Australia<br><br>
Vietnam 1969-70<br><br>

